#: src/LegalNoticeSupport.php:204
msgid ""
"The contents of my pages were created with great care. However, I cannot "
"guarantee that the content is correct, complete or up-to-date. I am "
"responsible for my own content on these pages according to general laws; "
"However, I am not obliged to monitor transmitted or stored third-party "
